{"expireTime":9007200824590751000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-html-c42bba8259a878f79102d0ca9a4c0978-gatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-images-medium-zoomgatsby-remark-responsive-iframegatsby-remark-prismjsgatsby-remark-copy-linked-filesgatsby-remark-smartypantsgatsby-remark-autolink-headersgatsby-remark-emoji-","val":"<p><strong>Hoisting</strong>이란, 선언을 현재 스크립트 또는 현재 함수의 맨 위로 이동시키는 JavaScript의 기본 동작이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>변수가 함수 내에서 정의되었을 경우 : 선언이 <strong>함수 내부의 최상위</strong>로 Hoisting 됨.</li>\n<li>변수가 함수 밖에 정의되었을 경우 : 선언이 <strong>전역 컨텍스트의 최상위</strong>로 Hoisting 됨.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"호이스팅-때문에-변수를-선언하기-전에-사용할-수-있다\"><a href=\"#%ED%98%B8%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%85-%EB%95%8C%EB%AC%B8%EC%97%90-%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98%EB%A5%BC-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"호이스팅 때문에 변수를 선언하기 전에 사용할 수 있다 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>호이스팅 때문에 변수를 선언하기 전에 사용할 수 있다.</h3>\n<p>JavaScript에서는 변수를 선언하기 전에 사용할 수 있다. 아래에 선언을 해도 선언한 것이 Hoisting 되어 위로 끌어올려지기 때문이다. 아래의 Code-1과 Code-2는 동일한 코드라고 보면 된다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"code-1\"><a href=\"#code-1\" aria-label=\"code 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code-1</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// x에 값을 할당</span>\n \nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 5</span>\n \n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// x 선언</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"code-2\"><a href=\"#code-2\" aria-label=\"code 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code-2</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// x 선언</span>\nx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// x에 값을 할당</span>\n \nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 5</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"할당은-호이스팅하지-않고-선언만-호이스팅한다\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%A0%EB%8B%B9%EC%9D%80-%ED%98%B8%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%85%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80-%EC%95%8A%EA%B3%A0-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EB%A7%8C-%ED%98%B8%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%85%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"할당은 호이스팅하지 않고 선언만 호이스팅한다 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>할당은 호이스팅하지 않고, 선언만 호이스팅한다.</h3>\n<p>JavaScript는 Hoisting을 할 때, 할당은 Hoisting을 하지 않고 선언만 Hoisting하고, 다음 Code-3과 Code-4는 동일한 코드라고 보면 된다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"code-3\"><a href=\"#code-3\" aria-label=\"code 3 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code-3</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// x를 선언하고 x에 5를 할당</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 5 undefined</span>\n \n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// y를 선언하고 y에 7을 할당</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"code-4\"><a href=\"#code-4\" aria-label=\"code 4 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code-4</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// x를 선언하고 x에 5를 할당</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// y를 선언</span>\n \nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 5 undefined</span>\n\ny <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// y에 7을 할당</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 Code-3과 Code-4에서 <code class=\"language-text\">y</code>에 할당된 값인 <code class=\"language-text\">7</code>이 출력되지 않고 <code class=\"language-text\">undefined</code>가 출력되는 이유는, 선언만 위쪽으로 끌어 올려지고(Hoisting), 할당은 위로 끌어 올려지지 않기 때문이다.</p>\n<p>Hosting으로 인해 <code class=\"language-text\">y</code>는 사용되기 전에 선언은 되었지만, 할당이 수행되지 않았기 때문에 <code class=\"language-text\">y</code>값은 <code class=\"language-text\">undefined</code>가 되는 것이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">foo</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Hello world!</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>foo 함수에 대한 선언을 호이스팅.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">foo</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ERROR! foo is not a function</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>변수에 함수 리터럴 ()</p>\n<p>Hosting은 많은 개발자에게 알려지지 않거나 간과 된 JavaScript의 동작인데, 개발자가 Hosting을 이해하지 못하면 프로그램에 버그가 있을 수 있다. 따라서 버그를 피하려면 항상 모든 범위의 시작 부분에 모든 변수를 선언하고 할당해야 한다.</p>"}